ng--title elementskit-section-title \">Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy<\/h2><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a01c8d1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a01c8d1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5432b7a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5432b7a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-417fef0 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"417fef0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;slideInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:100}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>At <strong>Shila Vive<\/strong>, we ensure that your Pure Himalayan Shilajit reaches you safely and on time.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Order Processing<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Orders are processed within 1\u20132 business days after confirmation.<\/p>\n<p>Orders placed on Sundays or public holidays will be processed the next working day.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Shipping Timeline<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Delivery usually takes 3\u20137 business days, depending on your location.<\/p>\n<p>Remote areas may require additional delivery time.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Shipping Charges<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Shipping charges (if applicable) will be shown at checkout before payment.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Delivery Partners<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>We work with trusted courier services to ensure secure delivery.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Delayed Deliveries<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Delays may occur due to weather conditions, courier issues, or unforeseen circumstances. Shila Vive is not liable for delays beyond our control.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Order Tracking<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Once shipped, tracking details will be shared via SMS\/Email\/WhatsApp.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy At Shila Vive, we ensure that your Pure Himalayan Shilajit reaches you<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-9042","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9042","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9042"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9042\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9049,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9042\/revisions\/9049"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9042"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}